  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/e510aed1a0a7a85bc704ff456425028b.poster.avif?t=1765355738\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/e510aed1a0a7a85bc704ff456425028b.webm?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/e510aed1a0a7a85bc704ff456425028b.mp4?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>A fast physics-based brawler where you'll get dozens of \"holy heck, did I just do that? that was so cool\" moments.</strong><br><br><strong>One-hit death</strong><br>One wrong move and you are out! With 25 weapons as dangerous to you as they are to your enemies, every battle feels like dancing on a razor’s edge.<br><br><strong>Web swinging & wall crawling</strong><br>Run on ceilings and ramp up wild speed using physics- based web swinging.<br><br><strong>Wild maps</strong><br>55 maps to keep your fights fresh with various physics obstacles or hazards, and you can always grab more from the Steam Workshop!<br><br><strong>Versus</strong><br>Battle friends and randoms in intense acrobatic showdowns or epicly clumsy battles.<br><br><strong>Co-op</strong><br>Fight off waves of enemies, slowly gaining various upgrades as you try your best to “avoid” friendly fire.<br><br><strong>Play alone</strong><br>Test your skills by completing a variety of themed combat and parkour challenges.<br><br><strong>Editor</strong><br>Design your own versus maps, parkour courses, and combat challenges to test yourself or your friends.<br><br><strong>Customization</strong><br>The spiders are bald - help them unlock cool hats by completing achievements!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/d78e0add9875de50bcf3d2682c22c830.poster.avif?t=1765355738\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/d78e0add9875de50bcf3d2682c22c830.webm?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/d78e0add9875de50bcf3d2682c22c830.mp4?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Disclaimer: this is not Australia simulator.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/e510aed1a0a7a85bc704ff456425028b.poster.avif?t=1765355738\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/e510aed1a0a7a85bc704ff456425028b.webm?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/e510aed1a0a7a85bc704ff456425028b.mp4?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>A fast physics-based brawler where you'll get dozens of \"holy heck, did I just do that? that was so cool\" moments.</strong><br><br><strong>One-hit death</strong><br>One wrong move and you are out! With 25 weapons as dangerous to you as they are to your enemies, every battle feels like dancing on a razor’s edge.<br><br><strong>Web swinging & wall crawling</strong><br>Run on ceilings and ramp up wild speed using physics- based web swinging.<br><br><strong>Wild maps</strong><br>55 maps to keep your fights fresh with various physics obstacles or hazards, and you can always grab more from the Steam Workshop!<br><br><strong>Versus</strong><br>Battle friends and randoms in intense acrobatic showdowns or epicly clumsy battles.<br><br><strong>Co-op</strong><br>Fight off waves of enemies, slowly gaining various upgrades as you try your best to “avoid” friendly fire.<br><br><strong>Play alone</strong><br>Test your skills by completing a variety of themed combat and parkour challenges.<br><br><strong>Editor</strong><br>Design your own versus maps, parkour courses, and combat challenges to test yourself or your friends.<br><br><strong>Customization</strong><br>The spiders are bald - help them unlock cool hats by completing achievements!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/d78e0add9875de50bcf3d2682c22c830.poster.avif?t=1765355738\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/d78e0add9875de50bcf3d2682c22c830.webm?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329500/extras/d78e0add9875de50bcf3d2682c22c830.mp4?t=1765355738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Disclaimer: this is not Australia simulator.</i>",
